\title{TPE Scheduling cont.}

\p{Notes from the second scheduling chapter of TPE are folded into the [[B8GC]] hub. The concepts introduced here:}
\ul{
  \li{[[4WG5]]}
  \li{[[AM8U]] (proportional share via tickets)}
  \li{[[HCJ7]] (deterministic version of the same)}
}

\remark{On Linux, the user can manually set priorities using \code{nice} and setting the \em{niceness} of a process in \closed-open{-20, 20}.}
